Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H0F1B27&\pos(630,266)}CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H0F1B27&\frz354.1\pos(796,274)}ROOM 2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for asking you here.\NI know you're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. But what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know that based\Nupon the Ten Master Clans' decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the Saegusa Family and Jumonji Family are\Ncooperating to investigate the vampire murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard something to the effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get right to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya, will you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are aware that Saijo\Nfrom Class 1-E was attacked, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the only one who wants\Nto know what in the world is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we find the criminal\Nand hand them over,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,this ordeal isn't over,\Nand we won't feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have just one\Nperpetrator or is it a group?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a personally motivated crime\Nor something infectious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we have these answers,\Nwe can't write it off as "case closed."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you know about the situation?\NHow do you plan on solving it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you tell me that, I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you promise to help us,\NI'll tell you what we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean\Nyou'll join our search team?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You may take it as such if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll tell you\Neverything we know at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, there are more\Nvampire victims than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We believe we're dealing\Nwith multiple vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The expanded range special\Ninvestigation team from the police
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is also helping us\Ntrack down the vampires,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's a third faction\Ninterfering with our efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful of them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you accompany us?\NIf possible, from tonight--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiba should work on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find any clues, report them to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so helpful that Major Kazama let us\Nuse the stratospheric security camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be good and wait here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will await your return tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely need your help soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Then, we'll be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a promise, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could it be at this hour?
